{"tid":1277864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［未fact check］建制派車啲老人家去撐警","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T12:03:06.000Z","uid":137009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c6da0d11e92210707a82699dfb02145b482dc3c8","tid":1277864,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"首先利申，我唔係第一手資料，亦無法fact check<br />\n只可以當故仔咁聽，或者其他巴絲打可以幫手做資料補充<br />\n<br />\n啱啱呢個星期六，朋友個朋友個八十幾歲嘅阿媽參加咗粉嶺某區議員嘅一日遊活動<br />\n點知個活動係車佢地去撐警<br />\n最後仲要打完齋唔要和尚，掉低啲公公婆婆喺對面海<br />\n朋友個朋友個要去接返佢媽返嚟<br />\n<br />\n雖然搵老人家充人數都唔係啲咩新聞，但係打完齋唔要和尚真係好過份<br />\n如果屋企有老人家，留意下呢排佢地參加啲咩活動"},{"pid":"59ec9acbde46bdb48b98958e52f274ffde491727","tid":1277864,"uid":21616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:03:48.000Z","msg":"<em>早兩日睇ig個frd講<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfi43QT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkfi43QT.png&h=5f19f2b4&s={SIZE}\" /></em>"},{"pid":"1c6d9350e2f0bfae145e5314521abb6ae8d9546f","tid":1277864,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VCUGC7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VCUGC7.gif&h=85de303c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歷史實會記得"},{"pid":"40c2a3999fdff23058565182a580937578ab6ae8","tid":1277864,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"議員姓乜"},{"pid":"878e39caf095d8de8503809140417b3ba2046da4","tid":1277864,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40c2a3999fdff23058565182a580937578ab6ae8","tid":1277864,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"議員姓乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:34:12.000Z","msg":"因為係第N手資料, 我都查證唔到"},{"pid":"6ab99c0e986f50870793e7386cb1cf7dc974afaf","tid":1277864,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T1